  "original_title": "\u0d91\u0daf\u0dcf \u0dc0\u0dda\u0dbd \u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0da2\u0db1\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9c\u0dda \u0db6\u0da9\u0d9c\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d89\u0dc4\u0dc5 \u0dba\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The hunger of the people increases with the control of Vela Tours",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Gamini Valeboda, member of the political committee of the National Freedom Front, said that a Vela Tours regime would only increase the pressure of the people day by day.",
        "He also mentioned that the current administration will be forced to resort to an all-party administration with a minimum common agreement program to get rid of this situation.",
        "The MP said that the electricity bill has increased by 300 percent and the water bill by 90 percent in the past and pointed out that the prices of essential goods have also skyrocketed.",
        "He also mentioned that it is necessary to present a short-term, medium-term and long-term program to boost the economy.",
        "Mr. Gamini Valeboda requested the government to provide maximum relief to the affected people."
      ],
